ad decided to pay a visit on one of his most favorite relatives.  He had just come from Demeter's orchard, and had plucked off a few of her most delicious apples.  He didn't think Demeter would mind.<br>
<br>
And as he walked up Athena's temple steps, happily munching on one of the loot, bits of conversation within the temple caught his attention.  Heightening his sense of hearing, he realized that a competition was about to begin.<br>
<br>
&quot;This is a good day,&quot; thought Hermes, as he hastened his steps.  &quot;Good food and good entertainment, nothing beats it.&quot;<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uthegreatapollo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Great Apollo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 84<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/1/01 3:11:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> And he will draw a crowd...</span><hr size=1> Apollo appears in a blast of golden light, standing next to Hermes. He arms were crossed, and one hand to his mouth as he munched away at some truffles. He smiled to Hermes warmly, knowing that in his brother he found a friend that also loved a good sporting event.<br>
<br>
&quot;I heard that the goddess of victory challenged the goddess of war to a...duel. ::he waves his hand around::... I just had to come and see it.&quot; he smirks. His eyes wander the temple and lie on Dionysus. He nodded over to him, letting Dionysus know that he knew he was around.<br>
<br>
&quot;How is your mother Hermes?&quot; he asked with a smile, popping another truffel in his mouth. He shook the blonde hair from his eyes, and began to sit down as a lavish sofa appeared under him. He outstretched his legs while eating, leaving just enough room for Hermes to sit. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/umeihao.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Meihao</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/1/01 5:32:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Let the Games Begin</span><hr size=1> Hermes was overjoyed that his big brother had shown up.  This was definitely turning out to be a very good day indeed.<br>
<br>
Hermes eagerly plopped onto the seat next to Apollo.  Handing over one of the apples to Apollo, Hermes happily continued to munch on his.<br>
<br>
Seeing that Dionysus was about to enjoy the fun as well.  Hermes levitated another one of the apples over to his fellow Olympian.  <br>
<br>
Hermes smiled slyly to himself.  &quot;Oh well, if these apples ran out, I know where I can get more.  If I don't get caught.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uthegreatapollo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Great Apollo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 86<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/1/01 5:46:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Let the Games Begin</span><hr size=1> Apollo chews on the truffel and examines the apple. He was on the same wave lenth as his younger brother. He sniffed it and he cracked a smile<br>
<br>
&quot;Been visiting Demeter I see.&quot; he laughed and bit into the apple. The rush of flavor overcame him and a smile rode across his lips.<br>
<br>
&quot;Good job.&quot; he nodded to his brother ruffaling his hair. He took another bite into the apple. <br>
&quot;Truffle?&quot; he hend out a bag of French or what it was at the time Gaulian truffles to Hermes, his words muffled by all the apple in his mouth. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uividionysusivi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IVIDionysusIVI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/1/01 9:33:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Another Day in A teemple</span><hr size=1> ::After seeing his 2 brothers he decides to greet them each with a hug :: Hello you two i see you came to watch also. Hermes i am deeply sorry for the cupid thing it has gotten out of hand and i am trying to make it a quick end. Please accept my forgiveness with this glass of wine ::hands a glass to Hermes, Apollo and himself:: this is to forgivness and a new future <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 94<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/1/01 10:00:05 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> a duel</span><hr size=1> ***Appears in a flash on blue light as I look around Athenas temple and head toward the other gods in waiting for the duel to begin.*** Hello, I got kinda of bored down in my parts of the underworld, and every mortal in the area had there nightly dosage of sleep, and when I heard the sound of eager voice for a duel, I knew I had to come!... ***does a belly flop into the air, and lands on a dark blue circular bed with light blue silk covers and a purple pillow, and then gives everyone else a pillow to use.*** <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=goddessathena>Goddess Athena</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(7/2/01 11:29:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=62.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> OOC Note About Athena</span><hr size=1> (Guys, if you'll notice at the top of this posting, the other Athena left about a month ago when the changes went about in TOG. Please understand this before it likes gets out of hand. Remember what Hera said: &quot;We can't go having two of the same Gods around now can we?&quot;<br>
